snippet.title: Fashion Thrifting at Panache || Amber Ashli
snippet.description:
#fashionthrifting #panache #amberashli 

Unboxing Black Fashion Designer | Pyer Moss | Amber Ashli

Watch in 4K or 1080p!
Thank you for watching your blessing!

Come along with me as I grab some goodies from a local consignment shop in CT called Panache!
-

My name is Amber Ashli.
I am an independent published fashion and personal stylist from NY residing in CT with my own clothing brand, ISTMSTYLES.
-

If you like this video please drop a comment, hit the like button, and don't forget to share and subscribe to my channel.
---------------------------
https://youtube.com/channel/UCcw8t2pV5eBRiMvpUo1InUw
